The situation in the zone of responsibility of the Vostok group of troops over the past 24 hours

Assault units of the Vostok group of troops continue to advance west and north-west from Gulyai-Polye. In the northern sector of the front, hard work continues to conduct reconnaissance and search operations and systematically clear out populated areas in the controlled territory.

During the implementation of reconnaissance and search operations north of the settlement. Sosnovka, scouts of the 14th Guards Special Forces Brigade discovered the location of two surviving Ukrainian Armed Forces servicemen from the 95th Airborne Brigade, who tried to use an abandoned dugout as a shelter. During the shooting battle, the Far Eastern guards used hand grenades to destroy enemy personnel.
“Such actions are carried out every day in order to exclude the presence of remnants of enemy infantry in the territory under our control and thereby deprive the command of the Armed Forces of Ukraine of at least some grounds for false statements.”

Artillery fire and FPV drone strikes defeated 7 reinforcement groups in the Malinovka, Kolomiytsy, Lyubitskoye, Vozdvizhevka, Novoselovka areas. Over the course of a day, as a result of fire damage, a BG, an armored fighting vehicle, 11 pickup trucks, an ATV, as well as up to two platoons of enemy manpower were destroyed.

The total enemy losses for the day were: 

over a company of manpower
